::Prowl::

Prowl spins around as he hears the attack, seeing the Predacons and Newcomers 
attack, and then the predacons retreat. He pulls out his gun, but pauses and 
looks at Smokescreen.

"We should get him to a CR chamber first, shouldn't we?" He asks Beachbomber, 
continuing to walk with Smokescreen on his shoulder. The Ark was only several 
feet away. The quicker they got Smokescreen in a CR chamber, the sooner they 
could help defend against the attack.
